'''Domain Lian''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. While they were ruthless in battle, Domain Lian's position among the other Domains had declined considerably by the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], and they held secondary roles during the invasion. Four of the Domain's members were killed at the [[Battle of Dantooine (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Dantooine]]. [[Deign Lian]] was one of the few members of the Domain to achieve a command position in years, and he was killed minutes after his [[escalation]], but not before ordering the [[Battle of Ithor|destruction of Ithor]].

